Package: cognitive3dr
Title: Query Cognitive3D Session Analytics Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Nicki", "Anderson", , "support@cognitive3d.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an R interface for querying session-level analytics data
    from the Cognitive3D API. Includes authentication, pagination, and tidy data
    output for VR/XR session metrics. Extract session properties, events, objective 
    results, and exitpoll data for comprehensive analysis of user behavior in 
    immersive experiences.
License: file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
